<br>
Went down Friday to do Kirn, who was up, with two pets.  However, he was AGRO from Sage's raid apparently.  We got to the revenant tower and before we got out of the first room, Kirn came down out of his perch and started beating up our raid.  Our only option was to kill him, before I was able to turn in the icon.  We also killed his AGRO pet, but that left another up top which we couldn't get to.<br>
<br>
In short, since I couldn't turn the item in, I missed out on the generated faction, so I need to go down there again, if for nothing else to turn in the icon to get the faction hits.  I got the ring (from killing him Friday), but its worthless without the faction.<br>
<br>
Checked this evening, and Kirn was not up, but that extra pet was, and we never made it up there on Friday to kill it.  I wonder if we can get the GM to repop the zone to fix the issue... <p>Tanuden <BR>
